{"version":"https://jsonfeed.org/version/1.1","title":"贪心 - Tag | SPAWN2PWN","description":"Hugo FixIt 作者，喜欢瞎折腾、造轮子、写东西，分享一些前端开发中的所见、所闻、所思。","home_page_url":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/","language":"en","icon":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/apple-touch-icon.png","favicon":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/favicon.ico","authors":[{"name":"Lruihao","url":"https://github.com/Lruihao","avatar":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/images/avatar.jpg"}],"items":[{"title":"HDU 1009 FatMouse' Trade（贪心）","date_published":"2019-04-12T16:43:19&#43;08:00","date_modified":"2026-07-03T18:39:48&#43;07:00","id":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/hdu1009/","url":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/hdu1009/","authors":[{"name":"Lruihao","url":"https://github.com/Lruihao","avatar":"https://gravatar.loli.net/avatar/fee47a2f4f2cc71f99a02b0a73ecfee0?s=32&amp;d=mp"}],"tags":["ACM","贪心","HDU"],"summary":"5 题目大意 题目链接\n老鼠有 M 磅猫食 , 有 N 个房间 , 每个房间前有一只猫 , 房间里有老鼠最喜欢的食品 J[i] , 若要得到房间的食物 , 必须付出相应的猫食 F[i] , 当然这只老鼠没必要每次都付出所有的 F[i]，若它付出 F[i] 的 a%，则得到 J[i] 的 a%，求老鼠能吃到的最多的食物。\n5.1 Sample Input 5 3 7 2 4 3 5 2 20 3 25 18 24 15 15 10 -1 -1 5.2 Sample Output 13.333 31.500 6 分析 老鼠要用最少的猫粮来换取最多的食物 , 也就是 J[i]/F[i] 越大越好 , 所以按照 J[i]/F[i] 进行降序排列 , 然后依次用猫粮来换取食物 , 当所剩下的猫粮不足以完全换取食物 , 能换多少是多少。\n","content_html":"\u003ch2 class=\"heading-element\" id=\"题目大意\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e5 题目大意\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"#%e9%a2%98%e7%9b%ae%e5%a4%a7%e6%84%8f\" class=\"heading-mark\"\u003e\n    \u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 